  "title": "Infant Care Teacher",
  "description": "<p><strong>Hiring: Infant Care Teacher</strong><br /><strong>Loving, patient, ECDA-certified</strong><br /><strong>Infant care experience a plus</strong><br /><strong>Singapore﻿</strong></p><p><strong>Job Role & Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Plan and carry out the daily programme, developmental and care-giving tasks as assigned</li><li>Attend to the health, hygiene and safety needs of the infants</li><li>Create a safe environment and provide the best possible care to infants under their care</li><li>Build and maintain good rapport with parents</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Obtained at least a Advanced Certificate in Early Years (ACEY) or Higher Certificate in Infant Care (HCIC), or its equivalent</li><li>First Aid Certificate recognized by ECDA</li><li>Minimum 2 years experience in similar setting</li><li>Good interpersonal and communication skills</li></ul><p><strong>Working Location: Islandwide</strong></p><p>Are you interested in learning more about the opportunity? Please contact Carol at ﻿<a href=\"mailto:carol.sun@peopleprofilers.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">carol.sun@peopleprofilers.com</a></p><p>Reg. Number: R25129558</p><p>EA License Number: 02C4944</p><p>﻿Job Reference6338VV35</p>",
